Feature: Product Sorting and Price Consistency on SauceDemo # features/sorting_and_prices.feature:2

  Scenario: Sort products by price from low to high                                          # features/sorting_and_prices.feature:4
    Given the user is logged into the SauceDemo catalog page                                 # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:6
    When they sort the products by "Price (low to high)"                                     # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:14
    Then the products should be ordered correctly from the lowest price to the highest price # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:21

  Scenario: Validate product price consistency in the shopping cart                      # features/sorting_and_prices.feature:9
    Given the user is logged into the SauceDemo catalog page                             # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:6
    When they add the product "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket" to the cart                     # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:28
    And they navigate to the shopping cart                                               # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:35
    Then the price of the product in the cart should match the catalog price of "$49.99" # features/steps/sorting_and_prices_steps.py:42

